self.title: CDISC SDTM Urinary System Test Code Terminology

definition: A terminology codelist to describe the test code for examinations of the urinary system.
name: Urinary System Test Code
preferredTerm: CDISC SDTM Urinary System Test Code Terminology

terms.definition: A measurement of the color of a biological specimen.
The condition of the donated organ or tissue. (NCI)
The linear extent in space from one end of something to the other end, or the extent of something from beginning to end. (NCI)
A measurement of the total number of renal arteries.
A measurement of the total number of renal veins.
